### End-to-End Pipeline Flow

  CV (PDF/DOCX)
      |
      v  [M1 Skill Extraction — Overall F1: 0.863]
  Structured Resume Data (skills[], education, experience)
      |
      v  [M3 Skill Normalization — F1: 1.000 | Speed: 50-100ms]
